                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/wri-hosts-coal-use-china-future-use-and-emissions-control-briefing-tianjin-china">WRI Hosts &quot;Coal Use in China: Future Use and Emissions Control&quot;, A Briefing in Tianjin, China</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/agenda_tianjin_coal_briefing_10-05-10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="85" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
